	* ser-tcp.c: Adjust includes.
	(tcp_set_cmdlist, tcp_show_cmdlist): Declare.
	(tcp_auto_retry, tcp_retry_limit): Declare.
	(TIMEOUT): Remove, in favor of tcp_retry_limit.
